<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>

    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Cinzel|Cinzel+Decorative|Roboto+Slab&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;
            background-image: url('/images/0.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #f4f1de;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', cursive;
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #ffe5d9;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px #000;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #f4f1de;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <p>At SYS (Show Your Sword), we are committed to protecting your privacy and safeguarding your personal information. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose your information when you use our platform.</p>

        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Morbi sit amet tristique metus. Donec eleifend at elit ut aliquam. Proin et bibendum justo. Vivamus vel metus sed dolor pulvinar pellentesque. Praesent nec euismod sem. Ut a tellus elit.</p>

        <p>Sed consequat, magna nec accumsan ornare, nisl odio lobortis elit, ut rhoncus sem elit at odio. Phasellus pulvinar metus in justo tincidunt, ut condimentum mi efficitur. Sed blandit et erat ac volutpat. Suspendisse potenti. Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

